performed about midway up on the steps. The 
freshmen and the sophomores would be on the walk

01:36.459 --> 01:48.293
between the building and the front first curve. 
And then the, I beg your pardon, it'd be just the

01:49.654 --> 01:55.761
freshmen that were on the first curve. Sophomores 
