02:14.671 --> 02:25.665
incident that's worth telling there is that the 
live oak trees on the space between the street and

02:26.320 --> 02:55.872
the

02:26.320 --> 02:55.872
furrier dorm were fairly close together and if 
some unsuspecting soul had the misfortune to

02:26.320 --> 02:55.872
leave his car parked where the the out practice was 
to be held why the one enough freshmen had arrived.

03:00.652 --> 03:04.156
They literally would pick that car up and put it 
over between the trees. And at the time, there were

03:05.017 --> 03:10.944
a couple of trees that just fit a car just about 
snowed. So when the owner of the car, he had to bring

03:11.906 --> 03:16.992
the yell practices over no matter what. And then 
whenever he came, he had the devil of a time getting

03:17.592 --> 03:22.358
that thing out of there. Now, yell practices were 
normally held how often? Well, during the

03:27.458 --> 03:44.081
football season,

03:27.458 --> 03:44.081
if it was a way game, then they were Monday, 
Tuesday, Thursday, Friday. If it was a home game,

03:44.102 --> 03:48.087
the Friday was a midnight yell practice. And was it 
held in the stadium, midnight yell practice?

03:55.277 --> 03:55.778
No.

03:59.234 --> 04:04.540
I'll

03:59.234 --> 04:04.540
tell you, I kind of have to hedge on that. I believe 
we're going. But that's the only time. They never

04:09.606 --> 04:12.530
got away any other time. What about Guyon Hall? 
What happened at Guyon Hall? Well, it was a sort of a

04:18.777 --> 04:22.041
formal auditorium. Of course, it wouldn't have 
very many people.

04:27.854 --> 04:38.727
Dedications or things like that were there, but 
most of the students didn't, weren't really aware

04:27.854 --> 04:38.727
of it, although that was a, it was served as a movie 
theater. Did you all have movies there regularly?

04:41.930 --> 04:44.533
For a reason or so, yeah. And was there chapel 
services?

04:51.601 --> 04:56.427
May have been, but I don't remember being there. 
Can you think of, were there religious activities

04:57.352 --> 05:07.028
related to the community that you remember? Did 
many students on the weekend go to a worship

05:08.631 --> 05:13.278
service anywhere? Well, various denominations 
had

05:13.298 --> 05:21.672
churches or I know

05:22.681 --> 05:48.570
that

05:22.681 --> 05:48.570
there were great football teams at A&M in your 
first years tell me about those about football

05:48.787 --> 06:14.895
season well

05:48.787 --> 06:14.895
of course we arrived there in september of 40 with 
the team being the national champions from the

05:48.787 --> 06:14.895
year before and we we thoroughly made the most of 
every opportunity we could to see the team. Of

06:21.718 --> 06:39.183
course, you had a student activity card, which was 
part of the

06:21.718 --> 06:39.183
enrollment process, which paid for all the 
athletic events, so there was no problem in going.

06:39.203 --> 06:43.009
And of course, there were special sections for 
Freshmen knew where they were to be, and the

06:44.052 --> 06:51.859
sophomores and juniors knew where they were to be, 
and seniors were always up around the 50-yard

06:44.052 --> 06:51.859
line. Where? Were you all on the east side of Kyle 
Field? Yes. And did the Corps... From the 50-yard

06:57.805 --> 07:00.987
line north. Did the Corps march in before the game? 
No, the march in was... I don't know when they

07:06.773 --> 07:11.537
began, but it was in much more recent times. What 
about halftime? What did the band do in those days?

07:17.397 --> 07:22.142
Well, the band, of course, was always exemplary.

07:23.404 --> 07:25.466
Was their routine similar to what it is now? Well, 
the difference is they would go through a block

07:26.747 --> 07:42.544
arrangement and in and out and cross over and so 
forth, and then they would end up and

07:43.520 --> 07:50.627
spell out the opposing team or school. They would 
trail out, and they'd end up spelling out the name

07:52.688 --> 07:58.154
of the school. And then, once that was evident to 
the crowd, boy, they would evolve in under Texas

07:58.174 --> 08:07.262
Aggies and Marshall Field. So they did Texas 
Aggies, not a block T. Normally it is. Spelling

08:13.861 --> 08:21.692
out, spelling out the, at least the home, the other 
schools just spell out their own team. We always,

08:21.712 --> 08:32.126
A&M always spell out the opponent and our Texas 
Aggies.

