And during those years, those pre-war years, 
particularly your freshman year, were any of the

08:32.146 --> 08:43.581
football players on the campus considered more 
glamorous? or were the athletes just like

08:44.236 --> 08:51.362
everybody else in terms of the way you felt about 
them? Well, most of them lived in

08:53.844 --> 09:13.922
Dawn 12, at least in 1940, and that way they could 
kind of be there and have their own meals in Duncan

08:53.844 --> 09:13.922
and Storm, but They were in the Corps.

